stimulus:
Welcome to the experiment!

In the first task, please imagine:

Your country is involved in a military conflict with another country.

You are the commander of your army and must make decisions in the conflict.

Specifically, as the military commander, you must decide whether to launch a missile to strike enemy.

You will face a series of scenarios. Please read each scenario carefully and make a decision.

The task will take around 10 minutes to complete.

Please pay your attention during the experiment.
